title: cant even get a game of black market brawlers
body: im a lvl 10 and i cant get a single game of black market, i was in queue yesterday for 25 mins before i signed off, wtf is wrong with this game? been in queue 8 mins so far this time, with an approx wait time of 1:34...

replies.body: It's because your a low level it will require a lot of newish players above level 5(I think) to have about 10 people playing at one time so Good Luck, since hardly any low level players play in special events.
